{"tid":317514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[住屋問題] 與奶波魔深情對話","createTime":"2017-07-11T13:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T05:09:53.000Z","uid":26422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9b23dcef82b0a0408ff25881cf17340d5fa8a9","tid":317514,"uid":26422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>福氣來架👍，一諗到係香港死做爛做買唔到一層300呎樓，一份人工養唔起冚家😅，喂！福氣來架👍<br />\n<br />\n港喱廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/180317_03cbd1af556a332f8883b810f17ea9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F180317_03cbd1af556a332f8883b810f17ea9e5.jpg&h=2b69eb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港喱廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/180708_88dcd7246e8e865267e2758d7e4fe249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F180708_88dcd7246e8e865267e2758d7e4fe249.jpg&h=1bc52cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我鄉下隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/583ti0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F583ti0i.jpg&h=c69a313e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n福氣到極點啦👍，係香港早死係一種福氣啊喂😍！安心上路🍻福氣到極點啦👍，係香港早死係一種福氣啊喂😍！安心上路🍻<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s1C99n7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1C99n7.jpg&h=82caafd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/181622_aa873e3657c613d2bdc11e3eaa988428.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F181622_aa873e3657c613d2bdc11e3eaa988428.jpg&h=fa038feb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奶波魔：樓價跌一半 港豬都唔會住多一呎！"},{"pid":"6d38114efb1cbd65519b80843eda916